room_title: Escape room "Santa's Naughty List" by The Greatest Escape Games in Colorado Springs
room_address: 801 South Tejon Street Colorado Springs, CO 80903
room_description: Oh no! You and your friends just got notification that you are on Santa’s Naughty list. Luckily you know a sneaky little elf that can help you gain access to Santa’s office for an hour while he’s at his annual meeting with all the other holiday mascots. You need to find the naughty list and escape Santa’s office before the time runs out!
